 Bisi Alimi, a homosexual rights activist, claims that a gay man was murdered in Lagos on Monday, February 21. Alimi, who identified the dead as Dave, claimed he was killed after allowing a man “he trusted” to spend the night in his bed, arms, trust, and affection. He wrote; Last night, a young gay man was killed in Lagos. His name was Dave. READ MORE: There’s Nothing Spiritual About Love-making- Bisi Alimi He was killed because he allowed a man he trusted spent the night in his bed, in his arms, in his trust, in his love. Every year, young gay men in Nigeria become a victim of very simple things of life; seeking love and companionship. Please, I beg you today and always, Say his name, Dave. See post below:   A post shared by Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) 